Third-Party API Notice

This software integrates with third-party APIs that are free to use but governed
by their own respective terms of service. Users of this software are responsible
for reviewing and complying with the terms of each API provider:

- Open-Meteo (https://open-meteo.com/) — Weather forecast and geocoding data
- National Weather Service (https://www.weather.gov/) — US weather alerts
- RainViewer (https://www.rainviewer.com/) — Doppler radar imagery
- OpenStreetMap (https://www.openstreetmap.org/) — Base map tiles

This MIT license applies solely to the source code of this project and does not
extend to the data or services provided by these third-party APIs.
